%% Data Flow Diagram: Guardrails Detectors
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant Orchestrator as FMS Guardrails<br/>Orchestrator
    participant BuiltIn as Built-in Detector<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant HF as HuggingFace Detector<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant Judge as LLM Judge Detector<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant ModelFS as Model Storage<br/>(PVC/Filesystem)
    participant vLLM as vLLM Server<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Prom as Prometheus

    Note over Orchestrator,vLLM: Flow 1: Built-in Detection (Regex/PII)
    Orchestrator->>BuiltIn: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>HTTP plaintext, no auth<br/>{"contents": [...], "detector_params": {"regex": ["email","ssn"]}}
    BuiltIn->>BuiltIn: RegexDetectorRegistry<br/>pattern matching (in-process)
    BuiltIn-->>Orchestrator: ContentAnalysisResponse[]<br/>detection, score, start/end positions

    Note over Orchestrator,vLLM: Flow 2: HuggingFace ML Detection
    Orchestrator->>HF: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>HTTP plaintext, no auth<br/>{"contents": [...]}
    HF->>ModelFS: Load model files<br/>(filesystem read, MODEL_DIR)
    ModelFS-->>HF: Model artifacts
    HF->>HF: PyTorch/CUDA inference<br/>(in-process)
    HF-->>Orchestrator: ContentAnalysisResponse[]<br/>classification scores

    Note over Orchestrator,vLLM: Flow 3: LLM Judge Evaluation
    Orchestrator->>Judge: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>HTTP plaintext, no auth<br/>Header: detector-id<br/>{"contents": [...]}
    Judge->>vLLM: Evaluation prompt<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (OpenAI-compatible)<br/>VLLM_BASE_URL
    vLLM-->>Judge: LLM response
    Judge-->>Orchestrator: ContentAnalysisResponse[]<br/>judge verdict + score

    Note over Orchestrator,vLLM: Flow 4: Prometheus Metrics Scraping
    Prom->>BuiltIn: GET /metrics (8080/TCP)
    BuiltIn-->>Prom: trustyai_guardrails_* counters
    Prom->>HF: GET /metrics (8000/TCP)
    HF-->>Prom: trustyai_guardrails_* counters
    Prom->>Judge: GET /metrics (8000/TCP)
    Judge-->>Prom: trustyai_guardrails_* counters
